Example: Athletic Apparel, Coats & Jackets, Dresses, Intimates & Sleep, Pants & Shorts, Skirts, Suits & Blazers, Sweaters, Tops & Blouses

If you will be translating the software into multiple languages, each category name will represent the 'key' in the key/value pair. Do not use spaces or special characters. Each category name will need to be added to the "CategoriesRegions.resx" language file and the translated 'value' can contain spaces and special characters.
 
Example: AthleticApparel, CoatsJackets, Dresses, IntimatesSleep, PantsShorts, Skirts, SuitsBlazers, Sweaters, TopsBlouses

data.name: FinalSaleFeeStyle_NonAggregate_Help
data.value:
With the Seller Final Fee tiers set to the following values...

$25.00 = 5%

$100.00 = 2.5%

$999,999,999,999.00 = 1.0%

If an item sells with a final price of $125.00 the Seller Final fee is calculated as follows:

($125.00 x 1.0%) = $1.25

If an item sells with a final price of $99.00 the Seller Final fee is calculated as follows:

($99.00 x 2.5%) = $2.48

data.name: FinalSaleFeeStyle_Aggregate_Help
data.value:
With the Seller Final Fee tiers set to the following values...

$25.00 = 5%

$100.00 = 2.5%

$999,999,999,999.00 = 1.0%

If an item sells with a final price of $125.00 the Seller Final fee is calculated as follows:

($25.00 x 5.0%) + ($75.00 x 2.5%) + ( $25.00 x 1.0%) = $3.38 Seller Final fee

If an item sells with a final price of $99.00 the Seller Final fee is calculated as follows:

($25.00 x 5.0%) + ($74.00 x 2.5%) = $3.10 Seller Final fee

data.name: FinalSaleFeeStyle_Flat_Help

$999,999,999,999.00 = $10.00

If an item sells with a final price of $125.00 the Seller Final fee is $10.00

If an item sells with a final price of $99.00 the Seller Final fee is $5.00
